立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"13b25e6dad8c7ef6de56ab1652cc1e1d2455fa04","tid":1554333,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c01dd5dab597bb383e1eec35fb0a6041e41334","tid":1554333,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d50d8da15f47f3259fbd266fa9bf3f4e155d94da","tid":1554333,"uid":300783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c82415ee8b10a721acfa450df971a2e7c98ff14f","tid":1554333,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"邊度有地鐵無巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"有嘅, 係少啲啫<br />\n批准你跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:56:43.000Z","msg":"大西北區內移動唔搭鐵係有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da940d3610267a095710502e7d50faf5078eb178","tid":1554333,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b25e6dad8c7ef6de56ab1652cc1e1d2455fa04","tid":1554333,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c01dd5dab597bb383e1eec35fb0a6041e41334","tid":1554333,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d50d8da15f47f3259fbd266fa9bf3f4e155d94da","tid":1554333,"uid":300783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":